Class FastConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • odase.ABoxReasonerConfig

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    FastWithRangeConfig

    public class FastConfig
extends ABoxReasonerConfig
implements KnowledgeBaseOptions
    This configuration is the default configuration used by the workbench. It avoids calling generating rules which are slow.

      • translateMinCardinalityAxioms

        public boolean translateMinCardinalityAxioms(int n)
        Description copied from class: ABoxReasonerConfig
        Translate min cardinality from OWL axioms into the following SWRL rule

        p(?x, ?y1) /\ p(?x, ?y2) /\ .. /\ p(?x, ?yN) /\ differentFrom(?y1, ?y2) /\ .. /\ differentFrom(?y1, ?yN) /\ .. /\ differentFrom(?y(N-1), ?yN) -> (p minCardinality N)(?x)
        The int argument is the min cardinality. This allows the translation to be turned on or off depending on the cardinality (you might want to disable the translations for cardinalities higher than a certain limit).

        Specified by:
        translateMinCardinalityAxioms in class ABoxReasonerConfig
